content.content: ? - Mabel Tolkien boarded the SS Guelph and returned to Birmingham, England with her two children, John and Hilary. Arthur Tolkien stayed in South Africa with plans to join his family when time permits.

? - Charles Leslie Wrenn, Inkling, is born.
